description: EchelonSeaport 1 Bed 1.5 Bath home with your Private Balcony & 1 garage parking. The "05" layout is the only 1 BR with 1.5 Baths and a Balcony @ EchelonSeaport! Southwest view overlooking the courtyard and landscaped terrace. Modern kitchen w/ custom white cabinets, oak wood plank flooring & top of the line appliances. The bedroom has spacious closets & a spa like primary bath. This is a unique opportunity to own the only 1 BR layout at this development w/ balcony & 1/2 bath. 2 levels of spectacular retail & restaurants w over 50,000 SF of resort-style amenities. EchelonSeaport residents enjoy 1 indoor pool & 2 outdoor pools, hot tub, Sky Lounge w patio, state of the art fitness facilities including an indoor basketball court, golf simulator & yoga studio. The 5th floor Club Level features a lounge w fireplace, library, private dining/wine room, & outdoor terraces equipped w grill stations & fire pits. Residents will enjoy 5 Star services 24-hr concierge, doormen, & 24-hr valet parking
